ZH: 我明天要去医院做手术。
EN: I am going to the hospital tomorrow for surgery.

ZH: 医院里的医生很亲切。
EN: The doctors in the hospital are very friendly.

ZH: 他在医院工作了十年。
EN: He has been working in the hospital for ten years.

ZH: 我的妈妈是一名医院护士。
EN: My mother is a nurse in the hospital.

ZH: 医院里的设施很现代化。
EN: The facilities in the hospital are very modern.

ZH: 请问医院在哪里？
EN: Excuse me, where is the hospital?

ZH: 昨天我去了医院看望朋友。
EN: I went to the hospital yesterday to visit a friend.

ZH: 医院里的病房非常干净。
EN: The hospital wards are very clean.

ZH: 我们需要赶快去医院诊治。
EN: We need to hurry to the hospital for treatment.

ZH: 她的爸爸在医院里工作。
EN: Her father works in the hospital.

ZH: 医院门口停着很多救护车。
EN: There are many ambulances parked outside the hospital.

ZH: 我忘记了医院的名字。
EN: I forgot the name of the hospital.

ZH: 这家医院的口碑很好。
EN: This hospital has a good reputation.

ZH: 我们需要找一个靠近医院的宾馆。
EN: We need to find a hotel near the hospital.

ZH: 她在医院里做了一次体检。
EN: She had a physical examination at the hospital.

ZH: 医院工作非常辛苦。
EN: Working in a hospital is very demanding.

ZH: 每个人都应该尊重医院的规定。
EN: Everyone should respect the rules of the hospital.

ZH: 我在医院等了两个小时。
EN: I waited at the hospital for two hours.

ZH: 这家医院有很多先进的设备。
EN: This hospital has many advanced equipment.

ZH: 我们需要定期去医院检查健康。
EN: We need to go to the hospital regularly for health checks.
